
https://pabloariasal.github.io/2018/02/19/its-time-to-do-cmake-right/

This is about making user library *findable* by users of it in a cmake way.

1. the repo for the sameple. 
https://github.com/pabloariasal/modern-cmake-sample

2. download rapid json. https://github.com/Tencent/rapidjson/

3. build the sample

4. install

keitee@kit-ubuntu:~/works/modern-cmake-sample/libjsonutils/build$ sudo make install
[sudo] password for keitee:
[ 25%] Built target jsonutils
[ 50%] Built target gtest
[ 75%] Built target gtest_main
[100%] Built target json_utils_test
Install the project...
